      "content": "im so sick of this warfarin. my doctor keeps making me go back for blood tests every week because of my diet and it's honestly such a pain. i read online that if i just eat way more greens like kale and spinach and maybe take some garlic pills i could probably get the same effect naturally. do u think i could just switch to that instead of the pills?",
